Z_2010695814_RC2H3LARFX6Z_RTRMADP_3_SOUTHKOREA-ROBOT-MONK/2026-05-06T054951Z_2010695814_RC2H3LARFX6Z_RTRMADP_3_SOUTHKOREA-ROBOT-MONK-videoSixteenByNineJumbo1600.jpg" medium="image"><media:credit>Yonhap News Agency, via via Reuters</media:credit></media:content></item></channel></rss>